{"type":"message","id":"3773d920","parentId":"2f6b244b","timestamp":"2026-04-02T20:20:18.265Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_GMP1ccRMZbfKXlJBaocl0W2R|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cecf81cbc08199b0182dd7ebe9297c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775161218258}}
{"type":"message","id":"53f1bee2","parentId":"3773d920","timestamp":"2026-04-02T20:20:18.273Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uEgzU4kxaqy6eOD0lga3GCwa|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cecf81cbcc8199bc194e5eb05c04c2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775161218265}}
{"type":"message","id":"4613cc1b","parentId":"53f1bee2","timestamp":"2026-04-02T20:20:18.279Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uSSe1fk9vlxOwVaork8W05Tk|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cecf81cbd88199be8bbd27967e3fac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775161218273}}
{"type":"message","id":"22e3ac87","parentId":"4613cc1b","timestamp":"2026-04-02T20:20:37.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating internal tasks**\n\nI need to assess if there's anything requiring my attention right now. Since it's early, I'm thinking about checking the git status for the daily workspace backup. My self-improvement sessions are planned for later, so it seems it's not the right time for that. My instructions say I should perform heartbeat checks and report new files if necessary. If there’s nothing needing attention, I could simply respond with HEARTBEAT_OK after inspection. Long checks aren't ideal at this early hour, though.\n\n**Reviewing active tasks**\n\nI should probably avoid inferring previous tasks, but I can check current active tasks and see if there are any due alerts. Since it’s still morning, tasks like news and pre-checks aren’t due yet, and self-improvement tasks aren’t urgent. I can check the quant mainline health when the heartbeat runs, but that might be more complex than necessary right now. I could determine if there's anything that needs attention and respond with HEARTBEAT_OK if not. Checking the workspace git status might be worth it too.\n\n**Considering backup actions**\n\nIf there are uncommitted changes, I think a silent backup action might be a good idea. However, the safe practices include keeping git hygiene in the workspace. My checklist suggests I should execute a git add/commit/push. But pushing involves external actions, so I need to ask for permission first, per AGENTS’ guidelines. Since the heartbeat indicates daily workspace backups, maybe I should check the status instead of pushing automatically. If any uncommitted changes need attention, I could report on that.\n\n**Executing tasks in parallel**\n\nI’m thinking about running quant mainline guard and git status, perhaps simultaneously. It makes sense to have one task in the workspace while the other checks the status of git. I want to utilize multi-tool parallel to optimize my workflow, using execs to execute them both efficiently. This approach should save me time and minimize downtime, allowing me to get both tasks done at once. Let’s get this set up!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_073f4bacc39a5f690169cecf843fb88199a680e456979a96ea\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzs-VorQFw2Pzh9HbGDomVyxCvSGgChcEFlndla9lnLnxQqroA6TZbt0cbruFRG-reqpmQDT1cPy8Y-yE1rgikZmmbsHtPJ5Bl3howeiSMEbbR2cYKuVxCBoLrdtyXpO-XymFKZh04LocXcBfx-G_y7Vc5s7wYpYvrqp45FUB3FdLlNBlQRhEMRejD_vQcemZmqG30iqYD91737sjFS773g4078uk2KAeGJhqWFo6p2g7__2jUzJdJOWq7Kifx11G6Iikad8_oJi_f0GcIsSIxSzEvUe6JMnYI7udX8VNrE47ZtennL2CANB2msk8Zv-dTzFgikL-_FToH-njWCoIE1cios1Z0c4eYhi2L2WYc-wQ69LP3YJPXs0Ju8m72NbSk1TFVAnmm3tHki2J0_8gWFL7NAB1ysrKvoky45CishMXB5NKS0ktrilk9k_XTvmzZisYGFcC6dTdI_I5-aFqsrOiTEvlwOpUzkJUcMtz4UnNYVgX9XdtKwKw9X10lm2SQEO7bJVS4kjMorxJqy_F1HPtIKQXOi3yFcmqMJGUMsE_i_HIi5wFSJdZCvdT8f72PZcmzl8tmqXDjIf1UDMXlXjrJTb_hRbZmJBfdlsIKejWYvT3ULZZ600T61kkEFyJFkqw9HZS4VIVluGTIwEG__b9mgWKzzH-WNW9KcNALw7pKzBQo0b9V02HiX265LZqCHo6LRQZRPEM_JObzdtTOWyfmeh87e6CC8n-AnFpIPfuqegXsj3Fw4yKhyDYccBTD0DnojQe3K0HaExAkkZay2pKCVLs8b5o1dEQ9G9wDIcIVo5EeokC74dclTj1iuX_vUHEVuSLg8gPzIFDgK8L-BMhyTawjyQ1-5Um5tGmEYDfiMNbUQniNhy3Wsqaa4SPXBzQalasUQCEtkgCVK1bHICjOMyWdXfyhSxWOzNXlhkIHKVF3Z6WN4WBSSzslTB9U43O2KHdcwtKxqBzMPUMhSqXEmSDzqn2QlfbADoTTvb3hs7ckYwHtANi-gVRNXykutYqUWFD96VmDG7sHh7CWeUp7DJdyJJQL5Y-QvMgmHDC0j0s_JJGHWYmaitbg7vpqllYfpb8-xWEsuJEsH7x6aWIfIUaNDZpawwnGPKhR_ird9PLlF9sdoDY9CDJBRPT2AaDwPKIzh-hpRSaj0q0HBbhkyjq31-y6wuEOR_krRTbLtxiDprC1gcgCJ51ibeCdVefqLZhZUDAcUMHbP8QZ_6P8lgthIi0ogvmmrP3ZQeRhGaEgPFtI7p9G_jsasB2fV6N8vV--ePLFefuYtXvC9Mx_b096KowEatVhyokmBTNxZEl00tLSenQ01dgG8US4T-UZ4u6_eCh983MZzNSZ28QZms8vqQg_yUrBCLBrtOuA5sXnGgzT8AdewT5ZnpiLXkJUi9zTi9z-sVzE1LYJ9dAwyjIMFhHnBuTuy4s098aNLoTfUA9j0m8BSyg8eI0ih9gkw3nSvfZu9RyeQXvSOBE-8D-HD7Dw7Nn0-o-xmC9BvjuLgg1FaWFXCSnZueEgRFMuz2LygLoRCBT6A_reesOAo-KpB_nA6JzK_1YfzyAL5_LOfod4OsSASBd-4M3aVSB3ZxlYC