e keeping git hygiene in the workspace. My checklist suggests I should execute a git add/commit/push. But pushing involves external actions, so I need to ask for permission first, per AGENTS’ guidelines. Since the heartbeat indicates daily workspace backups, maybe I should check the status instead of pushing automatically. If any uncommitted changes need attention, I could report on that.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Executing tasks in parallel**\\n\\nI’m thinking about running quant mainline guard and git status, perhaps simultaneously. It makes sense to have one task in the workspace while the other checks the status of git. I want to utilize multi-tool parallel to optimize my workflow, using execs to execute them both efficiently. This approach should save me time and minimize downtime, allowing me to get both tasks done at once. Let’s get this set up!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_CDbdbjM0iIwW6ndZr2c0p1Zd|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cecf955920819983ca9644e0261be3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw status --short","timeout":20,"yieldMs":2000,"security":"allowlist"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw status --short\",\"timeout\":20,\"yieldMs\":2000,\"security\":\"allowlist\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1KwqNU5mrHLgDtcmMjiG4epo|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cecf95594c81999ffccb9082010d9d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":120,"yieldMs":1000,"security":"allowlist"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":120,\"yieldMs\":1000,\"security\":\"allowlist\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1620,"output":858,"cacheRead":35968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"sto