"id":"call_b0fAxpjZ1JfXiQCyh8ZjVu2F|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cefe050da48199b8c653ceb7a72e78","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":120,"yieldMs":1000,"security":"allowlist"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":120,\"yieldMs\":1000,\"security\":\"allowlist\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":576,"output":648,"cacheRead":88832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90056,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775172973940,"responseId":"resp_073f4bacc39a5f690169cefdf725748199990a1a5b28b48bbe"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2daffd60","parentId":"3257fd7d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T23:38:45.482Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_mrhVRsGZguqvOzW6QVR3AVwP|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cefe050d8881999cd63fec8f885c92","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775173125480}}
{"type":"message","id":"71806d28","parentId":"2daffd60","timestamp":"2026-04-02T23:38:45.485Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xqM4agxOC9C21TL8bB5vUNbm|fc_073f4bacc39a5f690169cefe050d9c819989f546f6ac7cfa0c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: done\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-04-02 23:58\nUpdated: 2026-04-03 00:02\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲确认继续推进单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证执行链\nResume Entry: 先看 ACTIVE_TASK.md，然后查看 dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.json、paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json\n\n## Goal\n- 完成 dual factor conservative 档的单纸盘灰度验证执行链，并产出可复核的 shadow 结果与灰度结论\n\n## Acceptance\n- 生成单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证结果文件（json 或 md）\n- 生成 baseline vs dual 的单纸盘 shadow 对照结果\n- 给出可复核结论：是否具备进入下一步 default 档或扩大灰度的条件\n\n## Current\n\n## Next\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 23:58] 新建本轮 ACTIVE_TASK，任务切换到“单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证执行链”\n- [2026-04-03 00:01] 启动“单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证执行链”子任务，并产出 shadow 结果文件与灰度结论\n- [2026-04-03 00:01] 生成单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证结果（JSON/MD）并完成 paper shadow diff 对照\n- [2026-04-03 00:01] 得出 recommendation=HOLD：live shadow 改善，但 risk_off/halt_new_buy 从 True→False，需人工复核 guardrail 行为\n- [2026-04-03 00:01] 提交单纸盘 conservative 灰度验证结果，commit=1dfc9ba50\n\n## Evidence\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_gray_readiness.json\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_live_system_v1_dual_shadow.py\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_dual_shadow.py\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.json\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_single_panel_conservative_validation.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_shadow_diff_conservative_20260402.json\n- git commit 1dfc9ba50 feat(dual_factor): 双因子单纸盘conservative档灰度验证产出\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775173125483}}
