{"type":"message","id":"951499f7","parentId":"1c7fd9bc","timestamp":"2026-04-03T04:08:51.285Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Time: 12:08 PM. Outside quiet hours (23:00-08:00). Now in the day.\n\nACTIVE_TASK Status=done, no Next items, no blockers. Good.\n\nACTIVE_TASK completed items show:\n- conservative shadow 每日 cron 已配置（交易日下午16:00自动跑）\n- 当前市场 halt，governance PASS，各 profile 均正常\n\nThe health report still shows ALERT for morning news missing. But it's past 08:50 and the issue is the morning news pipeline seems broken. The \"主动提醒\" rules say I should report:\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n\n\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\nMorning news being MISSING counts as an ALERT. The checklist indicates I should proactively report this ALERT since it's a core quant ops alert. So I need to surface the morning news pipeline failure.\n\nBut I'm torn—the user seems focused on the conservative shadow task, and the health report alert is persistent. I want to follow the rules about not repeating old tasks from prior chats, but the morning news issue is a new proactive alert that needs reporting. The rules are clear: I should only proactively report three specific things, and the health alert is definitely one of them.\n\nLet me keep this minimal since the ACTIVE_TASK is done and focus on the main alert. The governance PASS and conservative shadow running daily at 4 PM are confirmed, so I'll just note the morning news failure and suggest checking the pipeline. minimal. The health report ALERT has been reported multiple times already. If I report it again, it's \"重复打扰\" based on \"若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\". But the data hasn't changed - it's still missing. Do I report again?\n\nI think: since the quant ops ALERT (daily strategy audit ALERT) is one of the \"主动提醒\" triggers, and the mainline health shows this as ALERT, I should mention it but very briefly. But I also need to be careful not to spam.\n\nActually, looking at the heartbeat more carefully: it says \"每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\" for the daily audit/enhancements/dashboard. The health report is ALERT because the morning news pipeline is broken. This counts as \"每日策略审计为 ALERT\" which is in the \"主动提醒\" list.\n\nBut the specific trigger is \"每日策略审计为 ALERT\" - is this the strategy audit or the overall mainline health? The mainline health contains the strategy audit check. And it's showing ALERT. So yes, I should mention this.\n\nHowever, I should keep it brief. The user seems focused on the conservative shadow task and probably already knows about the health alert. I'll keep it concise and actionable.\n\nFinal decision: brief alert on morning news pipeline + governance PASS note. Keep it very short.","thinkingSignature":"1f3f6eff84097526c55f9d351ae0857f0ed50da995d01110c033ab7fe9e3e377"},{"type":"text","text":"量化主链状态速报（12:08）：\n\n**✅ 正常项**\n- governance gate：**PASS**（已补签字）\n- conservative shadow：已配置每日自动跑（交易日下午 16:00）\n- 各 profile：均正常\n\n**⚠️ 需关注**\n- 08:50 晨报：状态文件仍缺失，晨报链路断裂\n- 量化主链巡检：整体 `ALERT`（主因即晨报缺失）\n\n建议优先修复晨报链路，再决定是否恢复后续自动发布。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74464,"output":722,"cacheRead":25846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101032,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775189309415,"responseId":"061e703db30c6b6b5a9ab7dfba171ad5"}}
