{"type":"message","id":"ea5c1b91","parentId":"83003271","timestamp":"2026-04-03T06:34:32.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time: 14:33. It's past the quiet hours (23:00-08:00), so I should be more active.\n\nACTIVE_TASK is done, so no need to spawn.\n\nThe quant mainline guard is still showing ALERT. The 08:50 morning news is still MISSING after multiple checks. This is now a persistent issue. Since it's past 08:50 and the morning news was supposed to be generated at 08:50, this is now a genuine alert.\n\nThe HEARTBEAT says \"主动提醒：每日策略审计为 ALERT\" - but the issue is the morning news being MISSING, which is part of the quant ops. The mainline health is ALERT.\n\n\nI need to check the morning news state file and the quant ops checklist. It's also a trading day (Friday, April 3rd, 2026), so the pre-market check window of 09:20-09:40 has already passed. I should examine what the quant ops checklist actually requires for the morning news at 08:50. The morning news is part of the Morning News Push section in the heartbeat-quant-ops.md file, but I'm not reading that file directly—I'm just checking the health report and the ACTIVE_TASK. Looking back at the alerts I've sent, I've already notified about the mainline guard alert at 12:08, and now at 14:33 it's been several hours. I think I've communicated the alert status before, but it's still not resolved. I need to decide whether to keep reporting the same issue or try to fix the root cause myself, but I don't have enough information about why the morning news state file is missing.\n\nThe heartbeat says to proactively report only three classes of things, and the alert is the main thing keeping me reporting. But maybe I should just do the quant ops checks myself now that it's past 08:50. The issue is the 08:50 morning news is MISSING and the state file doesn't exist. Let me check if I can read the cron jobs to see if the morning news cron is even configured, since that's probably why the state file was never created.","thinkingSignature":"d2a0ba98584917ab5eed5593370d6eb4017d187694120755636caebbd19958d7"},{"type":"text","text":"ACTIVE_TASK 已完成，量化主链仍为 `ALERT`。晨报（08:50）持续缺失已超 5 小时，需要检查根因。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ktk0iz62iqy1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"FILE_NOT_FOUND\"","timeout":10,"security":"allowlist"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ktk0iz62iqy1_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json, subprocess, pathlib, datetime\n\n# Check cron jobs for morning news\njobs_file = pathlib.Path.home() / '.openclaw/cron/jobs.json'\nif jobs_file.exists():\n    jobs = json.loads(jobs_file.read_text())\n    morning_jobs = [j for j in jobs if '0850' in str(j) or 'morning' in str(j).lower() or 'news' in str(j).lower() or 'market' in str(j).lower()]\n    print(f'Morning-related cron jobs: {len(morning_jobs)}')\n    for j in morning_jobs[:5]:\n        print(f'  - id={j.get(\\\"id\\\",\\\"?\\\")} type={j.get(\\\"type\\\",\\\"?\\\")} schedule={j.get(\\\"schedule\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\nelse:\n    print('jobs.json not found')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15,"security":"allowlist"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":76230,"output":768,"cacheRead":25846,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775198040780,"responseId":"061e9258cd7684e3e796bc76c5d407aa"}}
