{"type":"message","id":"18c551c4","parentId":"0c7d596b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:04:03.968Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time: 17:03 (Asia/Shanghai). This is after the trading session (15:30 close). The 16:00 conservative shadow should have run. Let me check HEARTBEAT and ACTIVE_TASK. Also the heartbeat says daily quant ops (audit/enhancement/dashboard) should run once per day - already done at 16:33. \n\n17:03 is within the \"quiet\" hours definition? No, quiet is 23:00-08:00. 17:03 is afternoon, so not quiet hours.\n\nThe conservative shadow cron was set to run at 16:00. Let me check if it ran and produced output. Also need to check ACTIVE_TASK since the previous heartbeat noted it was done.\n\n\nI'll run the checks in parallel to verify the conservative shadow execution and review the active tasks.","thinkingSignature":"790f223ffbf8cc71d3078a41237a4ae90eee7eb57102ffa1c7e71ccacef74a4e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_spcmknpldywx_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_spcmknpldywx_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_spcmknpldywx_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/live_system_v1_20260403.json 2>/dev/null && echo \"EXISTS\" || echo \"NOT_FOUND\"\nls -la /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/dual_factor_shadow_*.json 2>/dev/null | tail -5","timeout":10,"security":"allowlist"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_spcmknpldywx_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json | python3 -c \"import json,sys; d=json.load(sys.stdin); print('status:', d.get('status')); print('generated_at:', d.get('generated_at')); print('last_success_at:', d.get('last_success_at'))\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":10,"security":"allowlist"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":499,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":107702,"totalTokens":108275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775207024486,"responseId":"061eb5716093fe21b18ab0343e8f64ab"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ca6d207","parentId":"18c551c4","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:04:04.096Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_spcmknpldywx_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775207044088}}
