{"type":"message","id":"eb508ff4","parentId":"09d51c17","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:34:08.581Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Heartbeat at 17:33. Let me check what's due.\n\n1. It's after 17:00, and the conservative shadow cron was supposed to run at 16:00 but we just discovered it wasn't set up. This is a new finding from the last heartbeat that needs addressing.\n\n2. The ACTIVE_TASK is done (Status=done, Completed).\n\n3. Per HEARTBEAT rules: \"主动提醒 - 每日策略审计为 ALERT\" → I already reported this at 16:33. Should I repeat it?\n\n4. Per HEARTBEAT rules: \"只有三类情况主动汇报: 1.新文件/报告已落地 2.脚本已跑出结果 3.需要用户输入/授权\" - The shadow missing is a new finding that warrants reporting since it was discovered but not yet addressed.\n   \nI've already reported the conservative shadow not running and its implications. Now I'm realizing the cron job itself might not have been properly set up—the ACTIVE_TASK was marked complete and it said \"conservative shadow cron configured\" but I never actually verified that happened. That's the real issue I need to focus on. I need to figure out who owns what. The conservative shadow cron setup failed in a prior session, so that's the current blocker for the quant system. Since it's a real operational issue with a clear owner (quant advisor), I should report it even though I already flagged the audit alert. The key is that this is a new finding from my investigation, not a repeat of what I reported before. I need to check if the conservative shadow cron is actually configured from the 10:56 ACTIVE_TASK completion, since that's what I promised to deliver.","thinkingSignature":"7909cd168ff022c899eb14a2ba7f4d6a6de8de2db2033120bc31bbe5ad452fe2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_97dos00xcbcb_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_97dos00xcbcb_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_97dos00xcbcb_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\njobs = json.load(sys.stdin)\nshadow = [j for j in jobs if 'shadow' in str(j).lower() or 'dual' in str(j).lower()]\ncron_schedules = [j for j in jobs if 'cron' in str(j.get('type','')).lower()]\nprint(f'Total jobs: {len(jobs)}, Cron-type: {len(cron_schedules)}, Shadow/dual: {len(shadow)}')\nprint('All cron jobs:')\nfor j in cron_schedules:\n    print(f'  id={j.get(\\\"id\\\",\\\"?\\\")} schedule={j.get(\\\"schedule\\\",\\\"?\\\")} type={j.get(\\\"type\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\nprint('Shadow/dual jobs:')\nfor j in shadow:\n    print(f'  id={j.get(\\\"id\\\",\\\"?\\\")} schedule={j.get(\\\"schedule\\\",\\\"?\\\")} type={j.get(\\\"type\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\n\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":10,"security":"allowlist"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":685,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":109759,"totalTokens":110518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775208824523,"responseId":"061ebc793c48a06de96c5a1615b0cc4b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c65369b4","parentId":"eb508ff4","timestamp":"2026-04-03T09:34:08.689Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_97dos00xcbcb_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775208848681}}
